<view class="management-shell"><view class="management-page"><view class="search-box"><input class="search-input" placeholder="搜索商品名称 / 编号" placeholder-class="search-placeholder" value="{{keyword}}" bindinput="onKeywordInput"/><view wx:if="{{keyword}}" class="search-clear" bindtap="clearKeyword">×</view></view><view class="tips-text">选择后商品 IP 将更新为「{{name}}」；原属其他 IP 的商品视为迁移</view><view wx:if="{{loading && !hasLoaded}}" class="detail-card empty-state"><view class="empty-title">正在加载商品…</view></view><view wx:elif="{{!filteredProducts.length}}" class="detail-card empty-state"><view class="empty-title">暂无可分配商品</view><view class="empty-desc">换个关键词试试，或先去商品管理新增商品</view></view><view wx:else class="product-list"><view wx:for="{{filteredProducts}}" wx:key="id" class="product-card {{item.alreadyInTarget ? 'product-card--disabled' : ''}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="toggleSelection"><view class="checkbox {{item.selected ? 'checkbox--checked' : ''}} {{item.alreadyInTarget ? 'checkbox--disabled' : ''}}"></view><view class="group-cover {{item.currentIp ? '' : 'group-cover--unassigned'}}"><text class="group-cover-text">{{item.ipInitial}}</text></view><view class="product-main"><view class="product-title">{{item.title}}</view><view class="product-meta">当前：{{item.currentIpLabel}}</view><view class="product-tags"><text wx:if="{{item.alreadyInTarget}}" class="tag tag--muted">已在此 IP</text><text wx:else class="tag tag--current">{{item.statusLabel}}</text></view></view></view></view><view class="action-bar"><button class="action-btn" disabled="{{!selectedIds.length}}" bindtap="submitAssign">加入该 IP</button></view></view></view>
